<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102782577995440></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102782577995440><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=1&mid=102782577995440>RE: War weapons</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=1&mid=102782577995440#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=162718><span id= >Rieli</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>223 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Jul 27th 11:22 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.53]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have to disagree about Dark Elves being wimpy warriors.&nbsp;&nbsp;Dark Elf Warriors make &quot;lighter&quot; tanks then the ogre/barbarian/troll warriors, but while fighting I often see messages like this:<br><br>a monster trys to hit YOU, but misses!<br>a monster trys to hit YOU, but YOU parry!<br>a monster trys to bash YOU, but YOU dodge!<br>You slash a monster for 29 points of damage!<br>You slash a monster for 27 points of damage!<br>You slash a monster for 23 points of damage!<br>You slash a monster for 29 points of damage!<br>You kick a monster for 11 points of damage!<br><br>While Dark Elves have very little strength and stamina, I find that I am missed a lot.  Of course, I don't really know how decent my AC is.  My level 24 warrior has more HP than my 35 druid, which I find kind of sad ;)  I'm not extremely twinked, either.<br><br>About the 1HB thing, I haven't found any decent warrior 1HB's so far, nor have I seen any.  I know that some people like to keep all their weapon skills up, and for some classes that's a very good idea, but I don't find it necessary as a warrior.  The only skill I use is 1HS.<br><br>Have fun, and I highly recommend a dark elf warrior.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ganerin, level 39 Wood Elf Druid<br>Vinaelil, level 25 Dark Elf Warrior<br><br>Officer of the Rune of Flames guild on the Veeshan Server</td></tr>
