	   <tr><td colspan=2>there is however one reason as a warrior to advance even your 1hb skill.. <br>when you start going higher lvl raids.. and grping.. your cleric will be gettin tired of having to heal all 3 mellee at the same time in the group lol .. in fact if he has to.. your probably gonna die.. so what they do is MA .. now the point of this is for one person before being assisted to smack around the enemy a lil while.. to make sure that the agro is mostly tied to him.. we all know this.. what does this have to do with 1hb? 2hb? well sometimes we find ourselves pulling the agro off of the MA even after hes taken the first 25 swings.. because we are hitting faster then he is.. due to faster 1hs items of whatever.. ive noticed if you put a 1hs in one hand and a 1hb in the other you pull alot less agro because blunt items tend to have a much longer delay time.. just a thought.. most people just switch to a 2hs item.. which is really your best bet.. but 1hb will work to and will enable you to still be able to use two weapons.. 1hb is pretty lame.. but it can help sometimes.. due to most 1hb items selling cheap and having longer delay times<br>taygarr<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
