<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=102792474037511></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f102792474037511><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=1&mid=102792474037511>RE: War weapons</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=1&mid=102792474037511#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=124705><span id=Scholar>Deckert</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>21 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Jul 29th 2:39 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.70]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have to disagree with some of the above posts that recommend skipping 1hb and piercing skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;Although it is difficult to keep all weapon skills maxxed at lower levels (because you level so quickly), you will have plenty of time at later levels to have all weapon skills level maxxed.  <br><br>There are many nice war 1hb, and they generally sell for cheaper than slashers of same quality. This is because many people think it is not worth training, so there is less demand. There are also certain no-drop 1hb that a determined warrior of any level can get for free.  Goranga spiked club in Maidens Eye comes to mind.<br><br>Same story as far as piercers go...many nice options available. Use search feature of this site for many examples.<br><br>One post mentioned that 2hp weapons were a complete waste, but in certain situations the Centi Warspear is a great weapon and is dirt cheap.  The velium lances are also the equal to their 2hs counterparts in every way (plus they sport a spiffy graphic).<br><br>Im also a big fan of situational use of 2hs/2hb/2hp weapons. Good for agro management in certain situations, and when fighting critters with damage shields.<br><br>You never know when you might win a roll or be awarded a terrific weapon of any type. As a warrior, you should be prepared to use it effectively right out of the gate. Limiting yourself to just the best 1hs you can get is greatly handicapping your options as a warrior.<br><br>Next time you are in bazaar, type /bazaar and search for different war weaps for sale and compare stats/ratios/weapon type and finally prices...you may be surprised to see that the best bang for your buck may not be a 1hs.<br>&nbsp;<br>Frostpaw<br>Barbarian Warrior<br>51 seasons<br>Cazic Thule Server</td></tr>
